title: Chelsea Wolfe
itunes:title: Chelsea Wolfe
description:
I had the distinct pleasure of having the extremely talented musician, Chelsea Wolfe, on the podcast this week. We discuss all things Northern California, being a weirdo and making your music diverse. It was such a unique energy she brought to the podcast and I appreciated it immensely. Check out Great American Ghost and their new track, "Prison Of Hate" on Spotify. Their new LP is out on February 14. Visit Rockabilia and use the code PC100WORDS for 15% off of your order. The best place for all of your VIP experiences at shows is with Soundrink. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
